info.title: Swagger Petstore

tags.name: BEFORE_NEW
tags.description: Dispatched before a Document is created. This event bubbles. This event is cancelable.

tags.name: BEFORE_OPEN
tags.description: Dispatched before a Document is opened. This event bubbles. This event is cancelable.

tags.name: AFTER_CLOSE
tags.description: Dispatched after a Document is closed. This event bubbles. This event is not cancelable.

tags.name: AFTER_CONTEXT_CHANGED
tags.description: Dispatched after the active context changes. This event bubbles. This event is not cancelable.

tags.name: AFTER_SELECTION_CHANGED
tags.description: Dispatched after the active selection changes. This event bubbles. This event is not cancelable.

tags.name: AFTER_SELECTION_ATTRIBUTE_CHANGED
tags.description: Dispatched after an attribute on the active selection changes. This event bubbles. This event is not cancelable.

tags.name: BEFORE_DEACTIVATE
tags.description: Dispatched before the Application becomes inactive. This event bubbles. This event is not cancelable.

tags.name: AFTER_ACTIVATE
tags.description: Dispatched after the Application becomes active. This event bubbles. This event is not cancelable.

tags.name: BEFORE_QUIT
tags.description: Dispatched before the Application is quit. Allows the quit to be canceled. This event bubbles. This event is cancelable.

tags.name: AFTER_QUIT
tags.description: Dispatched when the Application is quitting. Since the quit has been committed, it can not be canceled. This event bubbles. This event is not cancelable.
